::GoldenEye::

She looked at him,"Your welcome."
She knew this wasn't something that any normal Pred from Cybertron 
said or did.  Let alone being helpfull.  She felt like she was going 
soft. Maybe being alone in the wild without any contact with other 
bots had made her forget her hard, corse predacon attitude.  

"I have never heard of any bot named silver fox.  I'm sorry. maybe 
the bots at the base we are headed for know her."  She couldn't 
believe she was trying to be optimistic.  She shook her head and 
helped him towards the pod, on the east coast of the North American 
continant.
